OL,5, Three Gwent Police officers have been  
OL,6, suspended after a watchdog launched an 
OL,7, investigation into claims of racism,   
OL,8, misogyny and homophobia in the force.  
OL,10,FIt comes after offensive messages were 
OL,11,Freportedly found on the phone of a     
OL,12,Fretired police officer Ricky Jones, who
OL,13,Ftook his own life in 2020.             
OL,15,FThe messages were discovered by his    
OL,16,Ffamily.                                
OL,18,FMr Jones's daughter said she was upset 
OL,19,Fafter learning of the suspensions via  
OL,20,Fthe media.                             
